java.util.Iterator<fr.lipn.nlptools.uima.types.Token>
public class BasicTokenIterator
extends GenericTokenIterator<fr.lipn.nlptools.uima.types.Token>

This class does not add anything to a simple FSIterator over Token types. However it is more generic to use it because this way any future implementation of a component using it can be provided with a subclass which implements a more complex case instead (e.g. ignoring some tokens, etc.)
